        "solution": "write eventId and report to Storage before upload",
        "proof": "the documented storage-first retry sequence"
      },
      {
        "problem": "privacy and duplicate triage",
        "solution": "on-device PiiScrubber plus eventId deduplication",
        "proof": "the scrubber code and GitHub mapping capture"
      }
    ]
